Three birds



At one point there were as many as nine helicopters parked in the air over our house, but this was the most I could squeeze into one shot.
Taken Monday, July 23, 2001, 04:52:32pm.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 806kb
Technical details: Olympus C700UZ, 1/800s @ F3.5, ISO 100, 38mm
